</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idp48794032"><problem id="fs-idp120611040">
<para id="fs-idp176277168">Skrifaðu kjarnahvarf fyrir hvert skref í myndun <m:math><m:mrow>

<m:msubsup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.5em"/><m:mn>84</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mn>218</m:mn></m:msubsup><m:mtext>Po</m:mtext>

